title: Cowgirl Tennis Picks Up Hard-Fought Road Win At Texas Tech - Oklahoma State Athletics
content: Cowgirl Tennis Picks Up Hard-Fought Road Win At Texas Tech  Oklahoma State Athletics
description: LUBBOCK, Texas. – No. 11 Oklahoma State's women's tennis started its conference road trip with a gritty performance on Friday, taking down No. 27 Texas Tech, 4-2, at the McLeod Tennis Center.
